{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act40side", "eventName": "相見歡", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "OR-6", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "勝肉火方", "storyInfo": "煌和驚蟄重新聚首，二人決定前往百珍宴。另一方面，對於炎國朝廷來說，歲獸一事已經到了不得不做出結論的時候，真龍即將在百珍宴上宣布他的決定。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "58_g12_ningfucourtyard", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1614_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#3$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1614_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你那位朋友這麼快就走了？也不留人家吃個飯？", "name": "寧述"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……她還有別的要緊事，不能久留啦。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#3$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1614_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從小到大，都不見你帶朋友回來，還想著可以認識一下。", "name": "寧述"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許，也算不上是朋友……", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#3$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老人看著垂頭喪氣的寧茵，想說些什麼，卻終究沒有開口，只是伸手拂去了她肩頭的落葉。"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#3$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1614_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快要走了，還有好多事放不下吧？", "name": "寧述"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……爺爺也是嗎？", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1614_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵呵，前些日子總盼著趕快回去，真要走了，看著這一草一木，又都放不下了。", "name": "寧述"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還記得嗎？當年就在這亭子裡，鋪一層沙，拾一根棍，一筆一畫地教你寫字。", "name": "寧述"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你當時和我說，來年，府上所有的對聯都要由你來寫。我陪你練了兩個月，最後你自己撐不下去了。", "name": "寧述"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1614_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "結果第二年，你還真送了我一副對聯。", "name": "寧述"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#8$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“花好月圓吃得飽，天長地久……”", "name": "寧述"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#8$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些事，爺爺都還記得。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1614_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪能忘啊……又是一年中秋，日子過得真快啊。", "name": "寧述"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#8$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wind", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1614_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們爺孫兩個是不是很久沒這樣聊過天了？", "name": "寧述"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#8$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……嗯。最近我一直出門在外，爺爺您也忙著接待客人，見面的機會都很少。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#2$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1614_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這次舉家離京，折騰得不輕。", "name": "寧述"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#4$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過回到瑯珆就清淨了，路上也有大把時間讓我們談天說地。", "name": "寧述"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#4$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1614_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你自己的那本書，終於要寫完了？", "name": "寧述"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#8$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#2$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "爺爺，我可能……不能和你一起回瑯珆了。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#2$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1614_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……何時做的決定？", "name": "寧述"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#1$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寧茵輕輕搖頭，身子卻往後退了幾步。"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1614_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "爺爺此次歸鄉，是葉落歸根，人之常情，家人都非常明白。然而路途遙遠，換誰也放心不下。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#2$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寧家人才輩出，每個人都為大炎做著舉足輕重的工作。相比下來，若要有一個人陪您回去，沒人比我更適合。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#2$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過話說回來，我本就是瑯珆遠房遺孤出身，多虧爺爺憐憫，才能在這寧府住了幾十年。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今前往瑯珆，也算是回到父母生前故居了。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1614_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當時你主動要求陪我回鄉……是這麼想的？", "name": "寧述"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……爺爺，我本來是這麼想的。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#2$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一切都合情合理，我幾乎都要說服自己了。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#2$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這幾日，為了為《百灶食珍錄》結尾，我抱著告別的心思，又一次遊歷了百灶的大街小巷。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……可我發現自己所有的回憶，都與這座城市有關。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能清楚地記得，院中那棵柿樹是哪年栽下的，何時的果子最適合釀酒。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有街頭巷尾的各家餐館，它們的廚師各自有什麼樣的脾性，同一道菜又有多少種不同的做法。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我突然發現，比起這座寧府的宅子，這座城市，才更像是我的家。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1614_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉……", "name": "寧述"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#5$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……怪我，怪我沒有早些問你的想法。這陣子都是我自作主張了。", "name": "寧述"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#5$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "爺爺，從小到大，您就是我唯一的親人。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當初我的確想和您回故鄉，而如今堅持留在百灶……也是因為爺爺您。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1614_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為我？", "name": "寧述"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#5$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……嗯。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#2$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我最開始加入太史閣，參與編寫史書時，有件事一直讓我百思不得其解。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大炎數千年的歷史，突然從某個節點開始，推廣文字，普及教育。一些研究用的碑文，最早也就能追溯到那個時期。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想，在那個時代，一定有人推動了這些變革。可我翻閱了幾乎所有資料，卻找不到一絲線索。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我有一種奇怪的感覺，大炎的史書上，彷彿缺失了一個人。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1614_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "寧述"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1614_1#6$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到有次，我在一間棋館遇到了個怪人，他和我講了關於“那個人”的故事。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我原先以為他只是個故弄玄虛的說書人，可是在後續的研究中，我漸漸發現，他和我說的那些故事，居然一一被印證了。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在他的敘述裡，“她”是個溫柔的人，為天下蒼生，付出了太多心血……可為何這樣一個好人，卻沒辦法在史書上留下一個名字？", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#9$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那時我才意識到，原來史書從來不是一個容器，而是一把篩子。能留下的故事，少之又少。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#2$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "爺爺……我想要記錄下您的故事。可是我回過頭來，卻突然發現，與您相伴幾十年，我竟然都沒有辦法清晰地寫下您……", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#2$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寫下您，是一個什麼樣的人。", "name": "寧茵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4172_xingzh_1#2$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寧茵終於抬起頭，直視著老人的眼睛。"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她期待著老人會回答，回答她沒有說出口的疑問。"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她等了很久。"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "58_g4_baizaomainstreet_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_reedmarshes", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "r"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "r", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1631_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有動靜！", "name": "大理寺官員A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1631_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "r"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "r", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1632_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1632_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪有動靜？", "name": "大理寺官員B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1632_1#1$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1631_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘶……總覺得聽到了什麼。", "name": "大理寺官員A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1631_1#1$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可能是這幾天見的古怪案子太多了，總覺得不知道什麼時候就有人要跑來鬧事。", "name": "大理寺官員A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1631_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1632_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這可是大理寺，哪個腦袋有問題的敢闖這裡？", "name": "大理寺官員B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1632_1#1$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別自己嚇自己了，站完這班哨就趕快下班回家了。", "name": "大理寺官員B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1632_1#1$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1632_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-400,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1631_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-300,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7, "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "-200,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "待會先從正門進……就說自己是來報案的，再在去等候室的路上找到樓層的地圖……", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1632_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "昨天那個等候室的窗戶朝北，大理寺正門朝南，背面是高築的圍牆。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1632_1#1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "麟青硯的辦公室在三樓……從窗戶翻出去，順著消防管道往上爬，不會被發現。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1632_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#9$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "-200,0", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等找到那傢伙，*炎國粗口*先給她一拳……！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1632_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowstormflp", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "sn"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_breezetree", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#10$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "-200,0", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰？！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovementsp", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#9$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "200,15", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_punchsp3", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_punchsp5", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "58_g4_baizaomainstreet_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_axehitscrape", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_scratchmetalwall", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "sc"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "sc", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1644_1#12$1", "posfrom": "-600,0", "posto": "40,-20", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "40,-20", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "w"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "w", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#11$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "麟青硯？！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1644_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "煌？！", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1644_1#10$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼在這裡？！", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1644_1#10$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我怎麼在這裡？我來抓你回去！", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你那身官服去哪裡了？", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1644_1#16$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我辭官了。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1644_1#16$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回到旅店看到你人不在，就怕你做蠢事，還真是怕什麼來什麼。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1644_1#16$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我們換個地方再說！", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1644_1#16$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "sn", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g13_yanlivingroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_drkcludsthdr", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "d"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.3, "channel": "d", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1644_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#9$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是說，這麼多年以來，顧筌其實一直都停留在寧府？", "name": "麟青硯"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可你是怎麼打聽到的……", "name": "麟青硯"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你就別管那麼多了。你能不能直接告訴我，這到底意味著什麼？", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1644_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寧尚書與顧筌一案的牽扯比我想像的還要深，之前他的證言顯然有所隱瞞。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1644_1#3$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然我一度懷疑過他就是行兇者，可是按莫不服的證詞，如果顧筌當年為舊案伸冤而被打入死獄，而寧述是救他出來的那個人……", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1644_1#3$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那他便沒有動機再次謀害他。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1644_1#3$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1644_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最關鍵的是……我之前從不知道，虞澄竟然早已與顧筌有過接觸。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1644_1#1$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一系列事情背後的關聯，可能比我想像的還要複雜。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1644_1#1$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還是很好奇，我爸當年孤身一人來到百灶，他到底是想做什麼？", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1644_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這才是最關鍵的問題……", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1644_1#1$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1644_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（煌對於顧筌的兩段人生一無所知……如果顧筌的確是當年案件的受牽連者，又為何要在十幾年後回到百灶，將自己置於漩渦中央？）", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1644_1#4$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（寧述的立場、虞澄的謀劃……這些問題還是沒有頭緒。）", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1644_1#4$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（我又該如何讓煌知道……）", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1644_1#4$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，你幹嘛又是一副欲言又止的表情？", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我們接下來到底該怎麼辦？", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1644_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "煌，昨天的事……", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1644_1#2$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了，我知道你們“職責在身”的人，時不時就要做點不正常的事，都懶得和你們計較。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要你別再說什麼為了我的安全，讓我一個人回去之類的蠢話——", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1644_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1644_1#2$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還打算趕我走？？", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1644_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "煌，你相信我，這件事，我一定會徹查到底……只是，你不能繼續留在百灶了。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1644_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按我之前說的，兩天內離開百灶，先去龍門的辦事處。那裡也不是久留之地，你整頓好就立刻再啟程，儘快離開炎國——", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1644_1#1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我絕不。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1644_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不相信我會繼續追查下去？", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1644_1#2$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我倒是信你，可你自己一個人沒有官銜，沒有身分，還怎麼查案？", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1644_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我會想辦法。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1644_1#3$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "虞澄可以辭官暗中調查，我也——", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1644_1#3$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我有一個主意。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們不如做得徹底一點。", "name": "煌"}, "figure_art": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1644_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你想怎麼做？", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1644_1#1$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "煌從口袋中掏出了一封信。"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是莫不服給她的機會，現在成了她們兩人的機會。"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1040_blaze2_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1644_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "反正我們東奔西跑也問不出個結果。", "name": "煌"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們去百珍宴，直接找真龍問個清楚。", "name": "煌"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_thunders_amb", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "58_g5_dragonpalace", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_301_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陛下，這是禮部擬好的百珍宴與會官員的名單。", "name": "太傅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_301_1#1$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "時值佳節，維多利亞、萊塔尼亞、拉特蘭等國也遣使節送來賀帖。", "name": "太傅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_301_1#1$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請陛下過目。", "name": "太傅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_301_1#1$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1239_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳……咳咳咳……", "name": "太尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1239_1#8$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陛下……兵部協同司歲台已經擬定了完整的作戰計劃。", "name": "太尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還請陛下……咳咳……過目。", "name": "太尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_301_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "作戰耗費的人力財力、戰後恢復諸事，都沒有與戶部商議過，這作戰計劃是如何擬定的？", "name": "太傅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_301_1#1$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "知道太傅大人和戶部繁忙，兵部就多操了一點心，打這一仗要用的人力錢糧，乃至工部戰後修復的花銷，這筆帳我們都算清楚了。", "name": "太尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正好，當著陛下的面，太傅大人一起看了吧。", "name": "太尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_301_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "錢糧物資能算，戰事一起，大炎子民要流多少血，這也是一筆能算清的帳？", "name": "太傅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_301_1#3$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1239_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那太傅的意思是，算不清，就不用算了？", "name": "太尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1239_1#4$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_chairrub", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wtchkgopenftstp", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "wt"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "wt", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_301_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "太傅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_301_1#1$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "太尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "秋天了……今年北方的收成怎麼樣？", "name": "帷幕後的聲音"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_301_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那場災害過後，大荒城已經儘快恢復了生產。今年的收成，和以往數年相差不多。", "name": "太傅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_301_1#1$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那……明年呢？", "name": "帷幕後的聲音"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_301_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陛下……", "name": "太傅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_301_1#2$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "生年不滿百，常懷千歲憂……可時間不多了。", "name": "帷幕後的聲音"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_301_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事繫大炎萬民生計，請陛下三思。", "name": "太傅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_301_1#1$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太傅大人，該議的事，內閣六部，早都不知道議了多少遍，總該到了拿主意的時候。", "name": "太尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陛下聖意已決，百珍宴上，等陛下宣布即可。", "name": "太尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_301_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "太傅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_301_1#1$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天色晚了，眼看要下雨的。", "name": "帷幕後的聲音"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……二位請回吧。", "name": "帷幕後的聲音"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "臣告退。", "name": "太傅&太尉"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_thunders_amb", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rainlight_loop", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "ra"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "ra", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帷幕後的人抬眼望去——"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "空蕩蕩的宮殿，高位之側，三張坐席並列擺設，居中的那張已經陳舊。"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一聲幽微的嘆息。"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "58_g1_yusrestaurant", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.5, "channel": "ra", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1621_1#9$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎喲哎喲……這雨怎麼說下就下，淋得我一身……", "name": "老姜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1621_1#9$1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一場秋雨一場寒……再過幾天都吃不上新鮮蔬菜囉。今年冬天的衣服都還沒來得及準備啊……", "name": "老姜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1621_1#9$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大廚，今年的冬菜說什麼也得提前開始準備了，你趁早把倉庫裡你那些亂七八糟的東西——", "name": "老姜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1621_1#9$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1621_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大廚……？", "name": "老姜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1621_1#3$1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "煌小姐？行箸姑娘？人呢……？", "name": "老姜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1621_1#3$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1621_1#3$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-200,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 2.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "d", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "ra", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "58_g13_yuskitchen", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_makesoup", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "m"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.5, "channel": "m", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "m", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "平常熱鬧的廚房此時空無一人，廚具也被歸置整齊，局促的空間看起來竟寬敞了不少。"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只有灶火上燉著一鍋湯。"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1621_1#2$1", "duration": 2.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "老姜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1621_1#2$1"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "m", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}